[src:uefi-secure-boot-deep/unified-extensible-firmware-interface] By 2019, all computers based on Intel platforms no longer have legacy PC BIOS support.
[src:uefi-secure-boot-deep/unified-extensible-firmware-interface] A operating system that can be booted from (U)EFI is called a (U)EFI-aware operating system, defined by (U)EFI specification.
